## $\Delta$Confirmed vs. Confirmed in log-log plot
The numer of new confirmed cases $\Delta C$ can be desribed as,
\begin{align*}
\Delta C=N^{-1}\beta (N - C) I
\end{align*}
This is because $C=I+R+F$ and $S=N-C$ in SIR-F model.

